issue.title: support for pytorch 1.3.0
issue.body:
first, this is a great package! it seems like to bring the only cool part of tensorflow (tf.data) to pytorch. Thanks for the effort.

Is torch 1.3.0 supported in the current release?

issue.title: Do not install requirements
issue.body:
Those are handled within tox environment now.
No need to install them globally with pip
